{"tid":507393,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［超級荀盤］屯門公屋業主賤賣公屋助連登仔置業上車","createTime":"2017-12-23T08:00:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-23T08:48:07.000Z","uid":39539,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"43be269cae8c47b0c6170ed8a5a7ef5b0d80c53b","tid":507393,"uid":39539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T08:00:33.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】本報接獲讀者爆料，指祥益地產網站顯示屯門公屋建生邨有業主以自由市場叫價800萬元放盤，形容為之震驚。<br />\n本報跟進發現祥益地產網站的確出現建生邨叫價800萬元的癲價放盤，單位實用544方呎，呎價高達14,706元，媲美市區部份藍籌屋苑。如荔枝角美孚新邨，中原數據顯示其現時平均呎價12,300<br />\n祥益地產黃慶德表示，該叫價800萬元公屋，為建生邨泰生樓高層8室，本月初才放盤，業主正辦理居二市場出售證，綠表亦天價放盤，開價400萬元，較市價約300萬元貴逾三成。代理解釋指該單位於自由市場竟開價800萬元，據知是因建生邨補地價折扣較高。<br />\n土地註冊處資料顯示，這間屯門800萬元公屋，業主1998年向房屋署僅以16.24萬元買入單位自住，若以是次綠表叫價計算，較其買入價加價近24倍。<br />\n目前全港最貴公屋是大圍顯徑邨，一個實用490方呎於今年11月以530萬元易手。代理表示，現時建生邨同面積連地價放盤不足5個，入場費約480萬元。鑽石山鳳德邨驚見叫價近600萬元的綠表放盤。富誠地產林凱薇表示，鳳德邨雪鳳樓高層3室，實用598方呎，居二市場叫價599萬元，呎價10,017元，挑戰全港最貴未補價公屋。"},{"pid":"d41743bf49622f6e4ec0a4ab18ef78db773f1dd3","tid":507393,"uid":126099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T08:05:20.000Z","msg":"800萬544呎 公屋 仲要 屯門<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fe37212e6364c130a63d211cd587c07a011baa1","tid":507393,"uid":26451,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T08:06:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"82ba9e1dd7356731a37bb86297056b1961f97545","tid":507393,"uid":46910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T08:08:26.000Z","msg":"連登仔月薪十萬 幾百粒少數目啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"297a2119d0d1e21ac9a77cde5894a2299db37225","tid":507393,"uid":65956,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T08:10:11.000Z","msg":"八舊買將軍澳私樓都得啦吓話<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"063f91e76c7d9f37390b132aecf7f2f297e2f4b1","tid":507393,"uid":13645,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T08:13:20.000Z","msg":"8 球買到荃灣萬景峰500 呎<br />\n仲住公屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c906cbf0437704a153692bd74a4aa5dcb20748da","tid":507393,"uid":32583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T08:15:06.000Z","msg":"大興都夠收佢皮啦"},{"pid":"54cce350bb159d9615ad700c8829458c71d98386","tid":507393,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T08:15:41.000Z","msg":"良心價"},{"pid":"211bf218dee3a3266077b2eca6d456406986cfdd","tid":507393,"uid":39539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T08:30:43.000Z","msg":"業主趕住移民去印度，8球手快有手慢無，出年要1000個先買到"},{"pid":"9875703b716c11a7cc970bc6014c74126aba8239","tid":507393,"uid":39539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T08:35:17.000Z","msg":"買左呢間公屋王，兩隻雞脾都係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/23/163515_b171e199bb938b039a6a862c35f28dd7.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F23%2F163515_b171e199bb938b039a6a862c35f28dd7.jpeg&h=b1654d8e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9a3a5ae14816dbef222c50d58edd83e47f378c9c","tid":507393,"uid":78165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T08:38:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5872f805125e9e9f17cb9f41d5a3a240638593b5","tid":507393,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T08:48:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}